{
  "Title": "An update for libxml2 is now available for openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP3,openEuler-20.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-22.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-24.03-LTS,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP1,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP2",
  "Type": "Security Advisory",
